===Interjection===
'''[[no]] [[duh]]'''
#{{informal}} An expression or exclamation that something is exceedingly [[obvious]] or [[apparent]], or that one would have to be extremely foolish not to realize something immediatately.
#:''It says here not to drive with the sun shade covering the windshield of your car.  '''No duh'''!''

